    <section class="page-1 section-3 sr-story-main" id="909977">
        <article class="sr-story clearfix" data-id="909977" data-url="/speedreads/909977/south-korea-investigating-reports-kim-jong-un-grave-danger-following-surgery" data-headline="South Korea investigating reports Kim Jong Un is in 'grave danger' following surgery" data-tags="[speedread,News]" data-publish-date="April 20, 2020" data-authors="[Catherine Garcia]">
            
            
                            <div class="sr-slug"><a href="/speedreads/section/all%20eyes%20on%20north%20korea">all eyes on north korea</a></div>
            
            <div class="sr-headline-section">
                <div class="edit-link">
	<a href="http://cms.theweek.com/admin/tw-admin/edit/909977">Edit</a>
</div>                <h2 class="sr-headline"><a href="/speedreads/909977/south-korea-investigating-reports-kim-jong-un-grave-danger-following-surgery">South Korea investigating reports Kim Jong Un is in 'grave danger' following surgery</a></h2>
            </div>

            <div class="sr-date">10:58 p.m.</div>

            <div class="sr-body-share-wrapper">
                <div class="sr-body" id="sr-body-909977">
                                            <div class="sr-image-section">
                            <a href="/speedreads/909977/south-korea-investigating-reports-kim-jong-un-grave-danger-following-surgery" tabindex="-1">
                                    
    
                
        
                

                
                
                
                
        
    <picture class="picture-wrapper sr-image">    <source srcset="" type="image/webp"/>        <img class="picture webpLazyInView" alt="Kim Jong Un." src="/bundles/twsite/images/empty-src.png" data-image="https://images.theweek.com/sites/default/files/styles/tw_image_6_4/public/gettyimages-1128203693_1.jpg?itok=OlKdF78c&resize=180x180"
                                            />
    </picture>
                                <div class="sr-image-credit">Manan Vatsyayana/AFP via Getty Images</div>                            </a>
                        </div>
                    
                    <div class="sr-text">
                         <p>U.S. intelligence agencies have received information that North Korean leader Kim Jong Un is in "grave danger" following surgery, a U.S. official with knowledge of the matter <a href="https://www.cnn.com/2020/04/20/politics/kim-jong-un-north-korea/index.html" target="_blank">told CNN on Monday night.</a></p>
<p>He was last spotted on April 11 at a government meeting, and was absent at a birthday celebration on April 15 for his late grandfather, state founder Kim Il Sung. Rumors swirled in 2014, when Kim Jong Un was briefly out of the public eye. Upon his return, he was seen using a cane, and South Korea intelligence determined that he had a cyst taken off his ankle, CNN reports.</p>
<p>Daily NK, a Seoul-based nonprofit that monitors North Korea, has reported that Kim is recovering from heart surgery, and his condition is improving. Officials with South Korea's Unification Ministry and National Intelligence Service <a href="https://apnews.com/f477033c5883c24d3583ad1fe8824e52" target="_blank">told <em>The Associated Press</em></a> they were unable to immediately confirm the CNN or Daily NK reports, and are investigating both. <a class="author" href=/authors/catherine-garcia><em>Catherine Garcia</em></a></p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="speedreads-share-section sr-909977">
                    <span class="fb sr-social-btn" data-url="https://theweek.com/speedreads/909977/south-korea-investigating-reports-kim-jong-un-grave-danger-following-surgery" data-text="South Korea investigating reports Kim Jong Un is in 'grave danger' following surgery"></span>
                    <span class="twitter sr-social-btn" data-url="https://theweek.com/speedreads/909977/south-korea-investigating-reports-kim-jong-un-grave-danger-following-surgery" data-text="South Korea investigating reports Kim Jong Un is in 'grave danger' following surgery" ></span>
                    <a class="email sr-social-btn" href="mailto:?subject=South Korea investigating reports Kim Jong Un is in 'grave danger' following surgery&amp;body=https://theweek.com/speedreads/909977/south-korea-investigating-reports-kim-jong-un-grave-danger-following-surgery" title="Share by Email" aria-label="Share by Email"></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </article>

